  "texts": [
    "Chicken Farma, refutes a CT that feed producers are intentionally altering their products to reduce egg production and inflate prices, pointing out that the real cause of decreased egg production and increased prices is the outbreak of highly pathogenic avian influenza (HPAI), which has led to the depopulation of millions of layer hens [73].",
    "This CT has been placed in the Medical family.7.",
    "Drug Trafficking CT suggested that the CIA and its operatives in the 1980s used crack cocaine-sold via the Los Angeles African-American community-to raise millions to support the agency's clandestine operations in Central America [74].",
    "This CT has been put in the Economics and Business and Society family.8.",
    "McDonald CT falsely claims that human meat was found in the freezers of an Oklahoma City McDonald's meat factory and about 90% of other McDonald's meat factories inspected a hoax that originated from the satirical blog Huzlers.com in 2014 [75]."
